Class SelectCardOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vdom.comms.SelectCardOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SelectCardOptions
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Gives information about cards that are selected by the player from the table (piles, hand, play) This clas gives information about the constrains set on the selection of cards, e.g. what type, cost, from which place
